{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "backend-auth-api-collection",
    "name": "Backend Auth & RBAC API",
    "description": "JWT Authentication + RBAC + API Security demo.\n\n**Demo order (RBAC Lesson):**\n1. Register → Login (role: user)\n2. Admin Dashboard → expect **403**\n3. Run `node scripts/make-admin.js {{email}}` in terminal\n4. Login again → Admin Dashboard → expect **200**\n5. Create Product → Delete Product\n6. Promote user to moderator → re-login as that user\n\n**Security demos:**\n- Register with invalid email → **400** validation\n- Hit login 11+ times quickly → **429** rate limit",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "email",
      "value": "test@example.com"
    },
    {
      "key": "password",
      "value": "password123"
    },
    {
      "key": "role",
      "value": "user"
    },
    {
      "key": "productId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "targetUserId",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health Check",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": [""]
        },
        "description": "Check if the API server is running."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Test User\",\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Create a new user. Default role is `user`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Register (Invalid — Validation Demo)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"\",\n  \"email\": \"not-an-email\",\n  \"password\": \"12\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Teaching demo: express-validator returns **400 Validation failed**."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.token) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "        console.log('Token saved');",
                  "    }",
                  "    if (json.role) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('role', json.role);",
                  "        console.log('Role saved:', json.role);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login and receive JWT. Token + role auto-saved."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Profile",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/profile",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "profile"]
            },
            "description": "Any authenticated user. JWT payload includes id, email, role."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "RBAC Demo",
      "description": "Run in order during class. Step 3 requires terminal: `node scripts/make-admin.js test@example.com`",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Admin Dashboard (expect 403 as user)",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "dashboard"]
            },
            "description": "Before promoting to admin: **403 Access denied**. After re-login as admin: **200**."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Admin Dashboard (after make-admin + re-login)",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "dashboard"]
            },
            "description": "Run after `node scripts/make-admin.js {{email}}` and **Login** again."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3. List All Users (admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const users = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (Array.isArray(users) && users.length > 0) {",
                  "        const target = users.find(u => u.email !== pm.collectionVariables.get('email')) || users[0];",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('targetUserId', target._id);",
                  "        console.log('targetUserId saved:', target._id);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "users"]
            },
            "description": "Admin only. Saves first user id to `{{targetUserId}}` for role update demo."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Update User Role to Moderator (admin)",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"role\": \"moderator\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/{{targetUserId}}/role",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "users", "{{targetUserId}}", "role"]
            },
            "description": "Admin promotes a user to moderator. Re-login as that user to get new JWT role."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
